Class MetaDataPropertyType

Namespace
NDSH.Geospatial.Gml
Assembly
NDSH.Geospatial.Metadata.ISO19115.Ed2003.dll

Represents a metadata property in GML, which allows associating metadata with a GML object. The metadata can be in-line or a reference to external metadata.

Properties

About

Gets/Sets the URI reference for this metadata property.

[JsonProperty("about")]
public string? About { get; set; }

Property Value

string

A string representing a URI reference.

Remarks

This property provides a unique reference to an external metadata resource. The value should be a valid URI.

Exceptions

UriFormatException

Thrown when an invalid URI is assigned to this property.

AbstractMetaData

Gets/Sets the metadata content associated with the GML object.

[JsonProperty("AbstractMetaData", Order = 0)]
public AbstractMetaDataType? AbstractMetaData { get; set; }

Property Value

AbstractMetaDataType

An instance of AbstractMetaDataType containing metadata information.

Remarks

This property contains an optional metadata object that may describe the associated GML element. It can be in-line metadata or a reference to external metadata.
